'''Brother-In-Law Shipping Company''' was an export company based in the [[Rafa system]] that primarily dealt in valuable [[life-crystal]]s&mdash;in [[4 BBY/Legends|4 BBY]], it was the only company that transported consignments of life-crystals.<ref name="sharu">''[[Lando Calrissian and the Mindharp of Sharu]]''</ref>

